{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775860622170,"sessionID":"ses_28675a45cffeJLGgpa3aDqF6IA","part":{"id":"prt_d798aa153001prxhYK2g4IifF7","messageID":"msg_d798a980e001AsKJybZnZPvAmP","sessionID":"ses_28675a45cffeJLGgpa3aDqF6IA","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-abeaf6759f4143fa868a3a375f64d1cc","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # delta-spec.md — AR-014: Valkey 存储实现\n2: \n3: ## Package: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`\n4: \n5: ## Delta Overview\n6: \n7: 新增 Valkey 后端实现，与 Redis 后端并存，用于持久化 sandbox 元数据。支持按 session ID 存储、检索、更新和删除，并提供基于过期时间和最后活动时间的索引查询。Valkey 实现使用 `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` 客户端库。\n8: \n9: ---\n10: \n11: ## 新增接口和类型\n12: \n13: ### Requirement: Store interface contract\n14: \n15: 系统 SHALL 提供 `Store` 接口，由 Redis 和 Valkey 提供商实现。Valkey 实现使用 `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` 客户端库。\n16: \n17: ```go\n18: type Store interface {\n19:     Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n20:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n21:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n22:     UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n23:     DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n24:     ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n25:     ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n26:     UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n27:     Close() error\n28: }\n29: ```\n30: \n31: ### Scenario: Ping verifies connectivity\n32: \n33: - **GIVEN** 一个健康的 Redis/Valkey 服务器\n34: - **WHEN** 调用 `Ping(ctx)`\n35: - **THEN** 实现发送 PING 命令并要求返回字符串 `PONG`\n36: \n37: ---\n38: \n39: ## 错误处理\n40: \n41: ### Requirement: Not found semantics\n42: \n43: 系统 SHALL 返回包级错误 `ErrNotFound`（消息 `store: not found`），当 session key 在读取时不存在，或最后活动时间更新指向缺失的 session 时。\n44: \n45: ```go\n46: var ErrNotFound = errors.New(\"store: not found\")\n47: ```\n48: \n49: ### Scenario: Get missing session\n50: \n51: - **GIVEN** 后端不存在 key `session:{id}`\n52: - **WHEN** 执行 `GetSandboxBySessionID`\n53: - **THEN** 错误为 `ErrNotFound`（Redis: `Nil`；Valkey: `IsValkeyNil`）\n54: \n55: ---\n56: \n57: ## 数据存储键设计\n58: \n59: ### Requirement: Session key naming\n60: \n61: 系统 SHALL 使用字符串前缀 `session:` 与 session id 拼接作为 JSON 文档存储的主键。\n62: \n63: ### Scenario: Key construction\n64: \n65: - **GIVEN** session id `abc`\n66: - **WHEN** 存储写入 sandbox 数据\n67: - **THEN** 字符串 key 为 `session:abc`\n68: \n69: ---\n70: \n71: ## 索引设计\n72: \n73: ### Requirement: Expiry index\n74: \n75: 系统 SHALL 维护有序集合 key `session:expiry`，成员为 session id，分数为 `ExpiresAt` Unix 秒数。`StoreSandbox` SHALL 添加成员并使用 sandbox 过期分数。`DeleteSandboxBySessionID` SHALL 删除成员。\n76: \n77: ### Scenario: List expired uses ZRANGEBYSCORE\n78: \n79: - **GIVEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)` 且 limit > 0\n80: - **WHEN** 实现查询索引\n81: - **THEN** 选择分数从负无穷到 `before.Unix()` 的成员，限制为 `limit` 条\n82: \n83: ### Requirement: Last-activity index\n84: \n85: 系统 SHALL 维护有序集合 key `session:last_activity`，成员为 session id，分数为最后活动 Unix 秒数。`StoreSandbox` SHALL ZADD 分数为 `time.Now().Unix()`。`UpdateSessionLastActivity` SHALL ZADD 提供的时间戳（或零时使用当前时间）。`DeleteSandboxBySessionID` SHALL ZREM 成员。\n86: \n87: ### Scenario: List inactive uses activity index\n88: \n89: - **GIVEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, before, limit)`\n90: - **WHEN** 执行\n91: - **THEN** 返回最后活动分数 ≤ `before.Unix()` 的成员，最多 `limit` 条\n92: \n93: ---\n94: \n95: ## 存储操作\n96: \n97: ### Requirement: StoreSandbox atomicity and validation\n98: \n99: 系统 SHALL 拒绝 nil sandbox 或零 `ExpiresAt`。系统 SHALL 在一个 pipeline/multi 块中执行 session key 的 SETNX、ZADD expiry 和 ZADD last_activity。系统 SHALL 如果批处理中任何命令错误则失败。\n100: \n101: ### Scenario: Nil sandbox rejected\n102: \n103: - **GIVEN** `StoreSandbox(ctx, nil)`\n104: - **WHEN** 调用\n105: - **THEN** 错误指示 sandbox 为 nil\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ## 更新操作\n110: \n111: ### Requirement: UpdateSandbox semantics\n112: \n113: 系统 SHALL 仅使用 SET with XX（key 必须存在）更新 session JSON 值。系统 SHALL 在此操作中不修改 expiry 或 last-activity ZSET 条目。\n114: \n115: ### Scenario: Missing key on update\n116: \n117: - **GIVEN** session key 不存在\n118: - **WHEN** `UpdateSandbox` 运行\n119: - **THEN** Redis: SETXX 返回 false → 错误 `key not exists`；Valkey: 响应非 OK → 同类错误\n120: \n121: ---\n122: \n123: ## 删除操作\n124: \n125: ### Requirement: DeleteSandboxBySessionID cleanup\n126: \n127: 系统 SHALL 在一个 pipeline/multi 中删除 session key 并从两个有序集合中移除 session id。\n128: \n129: ### Scenario: Full removal\n130: \n131: - **GIVEN** 一个存在的 session\n132: - **WHEN** 删除成功\n133: - **THEN** GET session key 返回 not found，ZSET 不再包含该成员\n134: \n135: ---\n136: \n137: ## 查询操作\n138: \n139: ### Requirement: List loaders tolerate missing keys\n140: \n141: 当按 ZSET 列出返回 session id 时，系统 SHALL 按 id 加载 JSON；如果字符串 key 缺失 SHALL 跳过条目（Redis pipeline GET nil，Valkey MGET 空字符串）而不导致整个批处理失败。\n142: \n143: ### Scenario: Orphan ZSET member\n144: \n145: - **GIVEN** ZSET 中的 session id 没有对应的 hash/string 值\n146: - **WHEN** `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs` 运行\n147: - **THEN** 该 id 从返回的 slice 中省略\n148: \n149: ---\n150: \n151: ## 活动更新\n152: \n153: ### Requirement: UpdateSessionLastActivity preconditions\n154: \n155: 系统 SHALL 拒绝空 session id。如果 `at` 为零时间，系统 SHALL 使用 `time.Now()`。系统 SHALL 在 ZADD 前验证 session key 存在；如果不存在 SHALL 返回 `ErrNotFound`。\n156: \n157: ### Scenario: Activity bump for unknown session\n158: \n159: - **GIVEN** 没有 `session:{id}` key\n160: - **WHEN** 调用 `UpdateSessionLastActivity`\n161: - **THEN** 返回 `ErrNotFound`\n162: \n163: ---\n164: \n165: ## 后端选择\n166: \n167: ### Requirement: Provider selection via STORE_TYPE\n168: \n169: 系统 SHALL 不区分大小写读取 `STORE_TYPE`；如果未设置 SHALL 默认为 `redis`。支持的值 SHALL 为 `redis` 和 `valkey`；任何其他值 SHALL 导致初始化失败。\n170: \n171: ```go\n172: const (\n173:     redisStoreType  string = \"redis\"\n174:     valkeyStoreType string = \"valkey\"\n175: )\n176: ```\n177: \n178: ### Scenario: Default redis\n179: \n180: - **GIVEN** `STORE_TYPE` 未设置\n181: - **WHEN** `Storage()` 首次初始化\n182: - **THEN** Redis 实现被构造\n183: \n184: ---\n185: \n186: ## Redis 配置\n187: \n188: ### Requirement: Redis environment and password policy\n189: \n190: 系统 SHALL 要求 `REDIS_ADDR`。系统 SHALL 要求非空 `REDIS_PASSWORD`，除非 `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` 不区分大小写设置为 false。\n191: \n192: ### Scenario: Password required by default\n193: \n194: - **GIVEN** `REDIS_ADDR` 设置且 `REDIS_PASSWORD` 为空且 `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` 未设置\n195: - **WHEN** Redis store 初始化\n196: - **THEN** 初始化失败，错误提示需要密码\n197: \n198: ---\n199: \n200: ## Valkey 配置\n201: \n202: ### Requirement: Valkey environment and options\n203: \n204: 系统 SHALL 要求 `VALKEY_ADDR`（逗号分隔的地址拆分为 `InitAddress`）。系统 SHALL 要求非空 `VALKEY_PASSWORD`，除非 `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`。系统 SHALL 在 `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE` 解析为 true 时设置 `DisableCache` 为 true；系统 SHALL 在 `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE` 解析为 true 时设置 `ForceSingleClient` 为 true。\n205: \n206: ### Scenario: Single address configuration\n207: \n208: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR=localhost:7379`\n209: - **WHEN** `makeValkeyOptions()` 构建选项\n210: - **THEN** `InitAddress` 为 `[]string{\"localhost:7379\"}`\n211: \n212: ### Scenario: Multiple addresses configuration\n213: \n214: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR=node1:7379,node2:7379,node3:7379`\n215: - **WHEN** `makeValkeyOptions()` 构建选项\n216: - **THEN** `InitAddress` 为 `[]string{\"node1:7379\", \"node2:7379\", \"node3:7379\"}`\n217: \n218: ### Scenario: Password required by default\n219: \n220: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR` 设置且 `VALKEY_PASSWORD` 为空且 `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED` 未设置或非 \"false\"\n221: - **WHEN** Valkey 客户端初始化\n222: - **THEN** 初始化失败，错误提示需要密码\n223: \n224: ### Scenario: Password optional when disabled\n225: \n226: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_ADDR` 设置且 `VALKEY_PASSWORD` 为空且 `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false`\n227: - **WHEN** Valkey 客户端初始化\n228: - **THEN** 客户端创建时不使用密码\n229: - **AND** `ClientOption.Password` 为空字符串\n230: \n231: ### Scenario: Password provided\n232: \n233: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_PASSWORD=secret123`\n234: - **WHEN** Valkey 客户端初始化\n235: - **THEN** `ClientOption.Password` 为 \"secret123\"\n236: \n237: ### Scenario: Optional client flags\n238: \n239: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE=true`\n240: - **WHEN** Valkey client options 被构建\n241: - **THEN** `ClientOption` 上的 `DisableCache` 为 true\n242: \n243: ### Scenario: Disable cache not set\n244: \n245: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE` 未设置\n246: - **WHEN** Valkey client options 被构建\n247: - **THEN** `ClientOption.DisableCache` 为 false（默认）\n248: \n249: ### Scenario: Force single client enabled\n250: \n251: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE=true`\n252: - **WHEN** Valkey client options 被构建\n253: - **THEN** `ClientOption.ForceSingleClient` 为 true\n254: \n255: ### Scenario: Force single client not set\n256: \n257: - **GIVEN** `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE` 未设置\n258: - **WHEN** Valkey client options 被构建\n259: - **THEN** `ClientOption.ForceSingleClient` 为 false（默认）\n260: \n261: ---\n262: \n263: ## 单例访问\n264: \n265: ### Requirement: Singleton access\n266: \n267: 系统 SHALL 使用 `sync.Once` 暴露 `func Storage() Store`；失败的 init SHALL 通过 klog 记录 fatal。\n268: \n269: ```go\n270: func Storage() Store\n271: func initStore() error\n272: ```\n273: \n274: ### Scenario: Single initialization\n275: \n276: - **GIVEN** 多个 goroutine 调用 `Storage()`\n277: - **WHEN** 它们并发运行\n278: - **THEN** `initStore` 恰好执行一次\n279: \n280: ---\n281: \n282: ## 存储的数据结构\n283: \n284: ### SandboxInfo 结构体\n285: \n286: ```go\n287: type SandboxInfo struct {\n288:     Kind             string              `json:\"kind\"`\n289:     SandboxID        string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n290:     SandboxNamespace string              `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n291:     Name             string              `json:\"name\"`\n292:     EntryPoints      []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n293:     SessionID        string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n294:     CreatedAt        time.Time           `json:\"createdAt\"`\n295:     ExpiresAt        time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n296:     Status           string              `json:\"status\"`\n297: }\n298: \n299: type SandboxEntryPoint struct {\n300:     Path     string `json:\"path\"`\n301:     Protocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n302:     Endpoint string `json:\"endpoint\"`\n303: }\n304: ```\n305: \n306: ---\n307: \n308: ## Redis 实现细节\n309: \n310: ### Requirement: RedisStore struct\n311: \n312: Redis 实现 SHALL 使用 `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` 客户端。\n313: \n314: ```go\n315: type redisStore struct {\n316:     cli                  *redisv9.Client\n317:     sessionPrefix        string\n318:     expiryIndexKey       string\n319:     lastActivityIndexKey string\n320: }\n321: ```\n322: \n323: ### Requirement: Fixed key patterns\n324: \n325: | Field | Value |\n326: |-------|--------|\n327: | `sessionPrefix` | `\"session:\"` |\n328: | `expiryIndexKey` | `\"session:expiry\"` |\n329: | `lastActivityIndexKey` | `\"session:last_activity\"` |\n330: \n331: ### Scenario: Redis operations summary\n332: \n333: | Method | Redis commands |\n334: |--------|----------------|\n335: | `Ping` | `PING` → expect `PONG` |\n336: | `GetSandboxBySessionID` | `GET session:{id}` |\n337: | `StoreSandbox` | Pipeline: `SETNX`, `ZADD session:expiry`, `ZADD session:last_activity` |\n338: | `UpdateSandbox` | `SET key value XX` |\n339: | `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` | Pipeline: `DEL`, `ZREM expiry`, `ZREM last_activity` |\n340: | `ListExpiredSandboxes` | `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:expiry -inf {before.Unix} LIMIT 0 limit` then pipeline GETs |\n341: | `ListInactiveSandboxes` | `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:last_activity ...` then pipeline GETs |\n342: | `UpdateSessionLastActivity` | `GET` (existence), then `ZADD session:last_activity` |\n343: | `Close` | `cli.Close()` |\n344: \n345: ---\n346: \n347: ## Valkey 实现细节\n348: \n349: ### Requirement: ValkeyStore struct\n350: \n351: Valkey 实现 SHALL 使用 `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` 客户端。\n352: \n353: ```go\n354: type valkeyStore struct {\n355:     cli                  valkey.Client\n356:     sessionPrefix        string\n357:     expiryIndexKey       string\n358:     lastActivityIndexKey string\n359: }\n360: ```\n361: \n362: ### Scenario: Valkey operations summary\n363: \n364: | Method | Valkey API |\n365: |--------|------------|\n366: | `Ping` | `B().Ping()` → string `PONG` |\n367: | `GetSandboxBySessionID` | `B().Get().Key(key)` → bytes; `IsValkeyNil` → `ErrNotFound` |\n368: | `StoreSandbox` | `DoMulti`: `SETNX`, `ZADD` expiry, `ZADD` last_activity |\n369: | `UpdateSandbox` | `SET ... XX`; success requires `ToString() == \"OK\"` |\n370: | `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` | `DoMulti`: `DEL`, `ZREM` expiry, `ZREM` last_activity |\n371: | `ListExpiredSandboxes` | `Zrangebyscore` with `Min(\"-inf\")`, `Max(fmt.Sprintf(\"%d\", before.Unix()))`, `Limit(0, limit)` |\n372: | `ListInactiveSandboxes` | Same on `last_activity` key |\n373: | `UpdateSessionLastActivity` | `Exists` key → int64 must be 1; then `Zadd` |\n374: | `Close` | `vs.cli.Close()` then return nil |\n375: \n376: ### Scenario: Successful ping\n377: \n378: - **GIVEN** 一个健康的 Valkey 服务器\n379: - **WHEN** 调用 `Ping(ctx)`\n380: - **THEN** `B().Ping()` 被执行\n381: - **AND** 结果字符串等于 \"PONG\"\n382: - **AND** error 为 nil\n383: \n384: ### Scenario: Ping connection failure\n385: \n386: - **GIVEN** Valkey 服务器不可达\n387: - **WHEN** 调用 `Ping(ctx)`\n388: - **THEN** 返回来自 Valkey 客户端的错误\n389: \n390: ### Scenario: Retrieve existing session\n391: \n392: - **GIVEN** key `session:abc` 存在且包含有效 JSON\n393: - **WHEN** 调用 `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"abc\")`\n394: - **THEN** `B().Get().Key(\"session:abc\")` 返回 JSON bytes\n395: - **AND** JSON unmarshals 到 `*types.SandboxInfo`\n396: - **AND** error 为 nil\n397: \n398: ### Scenario: Get missing session returns ErrNotFound\n399: \n400: - **GIVEN** key `session:xyz` 不存在\n401: - **WHEN** 调用 `GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, \"xyz\")`\n402: - **THEN** `B().Get()` 返回 bytes 且 `IsValkeyNil` 为 true\n403: - **AND** error 为 `ErrNotFound`\n404: \n405: ### Scenario: Successful store with all operations\n406: \n407: - **GIVEN** 有效的 `SandboxInfo` 且 `ExpiresAt` 非零\n408: - **WHEN** 调用 `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)`\n409: - **THEN** `DoMulti` 按顺序执行：\n410:   - `SETNX session:{id} {json}`\n411:   - `ZADD session:expiry {ExpiresAt.Unix()} {id}`\n412:   - `ZADD session:last_activity {now.Unix()} {id}`\n413: - **AND** error 为 nil\n414: \n415: ### Scenario: Pipeline operation fails\n416: \n417: - **GIVEN** DoMulti 期间 Valkey 连接失败\n418: - **WHEN** 调用 `StoreSandbox(ctx, sandbox)`\n419: - **THEN** 返回来自 Valkey 客户端的错误\n420: - **AND** 没有部分写入被提交\n421: \n422: ### Scenario: Update existing session\n423: \n424: - **GIVEN** key `session:abc` 存在\n425: - **WHEN** 调用 `UpdateSandbox(ctx, updated)`\n426: - **THEN** `SET session:abc {json} XX` 被执行\n427: - **AND** `ToString()` 结果等于 \"OK\"\n428: - **AND** error 为 nil\n429: \n430: ### Scenario: Update missing session fails\n431: \n432: - **GIVEN** key `session:xyz` 不存在\n433: - **WHEN** 调用 `UpdateSandbox(ctx, updated)`\n434: - **THEN** `SET ... XX` 不会创建 key\n435: - **AND** `ToString()` 结果不是 \"OK\"\n436: - **AND** error 指示 key 不存在\n437: \n438: ### Scenario: List with limit > 0\n439: \n440: - **GIVEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, 100)`\n441: - **AND** `before.Unix()` = 1710000000\n442: - **WHEN** 方法执行\n443: - **THEN** 在 `session:expiry` 上调用 `Zrangebyscore`\n444: - **AND** `Min(\"-inf\")` 和 `Max(\"1710000000\")`\n445: - **AND** 应用 `Limit(0, 100)`\n446: - **AND** 通过 `Mget` 获取所有返回的 session ID\n447: - **AND** 有效的 JSON 文档被 unmarshal\n448: \n449: ### Scenario: List with limit <= 0 returns nil\n450: \n451: - **GIVEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, before, 0)`\n452: - **WHEN** 方法执行\n453: - **THEN** 没有执行 Valkey 操作\n454: - **AND** 结果为 `nil, nil`\n455: \n456: ### Scenario: Orphan ZSET member skipped\n457: \n458: - **GIVEN** ZSET 包含 session id `orphan`\n459: - **AND** key `session:orphan` 不存在\n460: - **WHEN** `Mget` 为该 key 返回空\n461: - **THEN** `orphan` 从结果 slice 中省略\n462: - **AND** 其他有效的 session 被包含\n463: \n464: ### Scenario: Activity bump for existing session\n465: \n466: - **GIVEN** key `session:abc` 存在\n467: - **AND** `at` = 2024-04-10T12:00:00Z\n468: - **WHEN** 调用 `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"abc\", at)`\n469: - **THEN** `Exists().Key(\"session:abc\")` 返回 1\n470: - **AND** `Zadd session:last_activity {at.Unix()} abc` 被执行\n471: - **AND** error 为 nil\n472: \n473: ### Scenario: Activity bump for missing session returns ErrNotFound\n474: \n475: - **GIVEN** key `session:xyz` 不存在\n476: - **WHEN** 调用 `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"xyz\", at)`\n477: - **THEN** `Exists()` 返回 0\n478: - **AND** `Zadd` 未执行\n479: - **AND** error 为 `ErrNotFound`\n480: \n481: ### Scenario: Zero time uses current time\n482: \n483: - **GIVEN** 存在的 session `abc`\n484: - **AND** `at.IsZero()` 为 true\n485: - **WHEN** 调用 `UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx, \"abc\", at)`\n486: - **THEN** `Zadd` 分数使用 `time.Now().Unix()`\n487: \n488: ### Scenario: Successful close\n489: \n490: - **GIVEN** 打开的 Valkey 客户端\n491: - **WHEN** 调用 `Close()`\n492: - **THEN** `vs.cli.Close()` 被执行\n493: - **AND** error 为 nil\n494: \n495: ---\n496: \n497: ## 依赖项\n498: \n499: ### Requirement: Package imports\n500: \n501: ```go\n502: import (\n503:     \"context\"\n504:     \"time\"\n505:     \"sync\"\n506: \n507:     \"github.com/redis/go-redis/v9\"\n508:     \"github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go\"\n509:     \"k8s.io/klog/v2\"\n510:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\"\n511: )\n512: ```\n513: \n514: ---\n515: \n516: ## Redis 和 Valkey 实现的差异\n517: \n518: | 方面 | Redis | Valkey |\n519: |------|-------|--------|\n520: | 客户端库 | `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9` | `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` |\n521: | Ping 方法 | `Ping(ctx)` 通过命令结果返回 `PONG` | `B().Ping()` 返回字符串 |\n522: | Get nil 检测 | `redis.Nil` 错误 | 在 bytes 结果上调用 `IsValkeyNil()` |\n523: | Pipeline/Multi | `cli.Pipeline()` 或 `TxPipeline()` | `DoMulti()` 执行多个命令 |\n524: | SETXX 成功检查 | Boolean 结果 | `ToString() == \"OK\"` |\n525: | ZRANGEBYSCORE | 带有 `RangeBy` 选项的客户端方法 | `Zrangebyscore` 带有 `Min()`, `Max()`, `Limit()` |\n526: | 批量 GET | `cli.MGet(keys)` | `Mget(keys)` |\n527: | Key 存在性 | `cli.Exists(ctx, key)` | `Exists().Key(key)` |\n528: | 地址配置 | 单个 `Addr` 字符串 | `InitAddress` 字符串 slice |\n529: | 可选标志 | 无 | `DisableCache`, `ForceSingleClient` |\n530: | 连接选项 | `redis.Options` 结构 | `valkey.ClientOption` 结构 |\n\n(End of file - total 530 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# delta-spec.md — AR-014: Valkey 存储实现\n\n## Package: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`\n\n## Delta Overview\n\n新增 Valkey 后端实现，与 Redis 后端并存，用于持久化 sandbox 元数据。支持按 session ID 存储、检索、更新和删除，并提供基于过期时间和最后活动时间的索引查询。Valkey 实现使用 `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` 客户端库。\n\n---\n\n## 新增接口和类型\n\n### Requirement: Store interface contract\n\n系统 SHALL 提供 `Store` 接口，由 Redis 和 Valkey 提供商实现。Valkey 实现使用 `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go` 客户端库。\n\n```go\ntype Store interface {\n    Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n    GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775860622157,"end":1775860622168}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775860622172,"sessionID":"ses_28675a45cffeJLGgpa3aDqF6IA","part":{"id":"prt_d798aa333001bcue4RHbmtcTd2","messageID":"msg_d798a980e001AsKJybZnZPvAmP","sessionID":"ses_28675a45cffeJLGgpa3aDqF6IA","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-943374a6b749496da11b73307a1631e0","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n2: \n3: > Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n4: > Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n5: \n6: ## Purpose\n7: \n8: AgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\n9: It provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\n10: session-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n11: \n12: ## Tech Stack\n13: \n14: | Layer | Technology |\n15: |-------|-----------|\n16: | Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n17: | Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n18: | HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n19: | Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n20: | Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |\n21: | Auth | JWT RS256 (golang-jwt/v5), K8s TokenReview |\n22: | Packaging | Helm 3, multi-stage Docker, GitHub Actions CI/CD |\n23: | Docs | Docusaurus 3.x |\n24: \n25: ## Architecture\n26: \n27: ```\n28: Client / SDK / CLI\n29:   → Router (Deployment :8080)\n30:      ↔ Redis/Valkey (session store)\n31:      → WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n32:         ↔ Redis/Valkey\n33:         → K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n34:   Sandbox Pods (with optional PicoD daemon)\n35:   Agentd (idle cleanup controller)\n36:   Optional: Volcano vc-agent-scheduler\n37: ```\n38: \n39: ## Conventions\n40: \n41: - Go packages under `pkg/`, binaries under `cmd/`\n42: - Python CLI at `cmd/cli/`, SDK at `sdk-python/`\n43: - JSON tags use camelCase; Go structs use PascalCase\n44: - K8s resources use `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` API group\n45: - Normative language: SHALL = mandatory, SHOULD = recommended, MAY = optional\n\n(End of file - total 45 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube — OpenSpec Project Context\n\n> Source: [github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube](https://github.com/ShijunDeng/agentcube)\n> Generated: 2026-03-21 (from source tree reverse-engineering)\n\n## Purpose\n\nAgentCube is a Kubernetes-native sandbox orchestration platform for AI agents.\nIt provisions isolated sandbox pods on demand, routes HTTP traffic to them through\nsession-aware proxies, and manages their lifecycle (creation, expiry, idle cleanup).\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n| Layer | Technology |\n|-------|-----------|\n| Language (server) | Go 1.24, module `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` |\n| Language (CLI/SDK) | Python ≥3.10 |\n| HTTP framework | Gin (Go), Typer (Python CLI), FastAPI (example) |\n| Kubernetes | CRDs (`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`), controller-runtime, `sigs.k8s.io/agent-sandbox` |\n| Storage | Redis (go-redis/v9), Valkey (valkey-go) |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/project.md","time":{"start":1775860622159,"end":1775860622170}}}}
